 Tavcor Audi has appointed Joel Epstein as the Sales Manager, New Car Sales, at their dealership on the Moffett Expressway. Epstein has a wealth of experience in automotive sales, having worked his way through the ranks at other premium brands. “I look forward to my new position at the Audi Centre, Port Elizabeth with great enthusiasm and am very excited to be part of the Tavcor Motor Group” said Epstein. Epstein can be contacted on tel. number 041 404 9400 or joel.ep.tavcor.co.za. 